				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${k}_{{ij}}={x}_{{ij}}\log (I/{I}_{j})$$\end{document}kij=xijlog(I/Ij)where, Kij represent the relevance value of a property j for a concept i, xij is the production frequency of property j over concept i, I is the total number of concepts in our dataset (I = 10), and Ij represents the number of concepts of the database for which property j was listed. Note that log(I/Ij) is equivalent to distinctiveness118.
